## Dependencies

- **cryptography**: Core encryption functionality
- **PyNaCl**: X25519 and libsodium bindings
- **asyncio**: Asynchronous I/O operations
- **rich**: Rich CLI interface
- **psutil**: Secure memory management
- **pytest**: Testing framework

